        "comment": {
            "name": "comment",
            "type": "com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.CommentSystemField",
            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/12583",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=arikon",
                        "name": "arikon",
                        "displayName": "Sergey Belov",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Patch here\n{code}\nIndex: library\/Zend\/Db\/Select.php\n===================================================================\n--- library\/Zend\/Db\/Select.php\t(revision 3290)\n+++ library\/Zend\/Db\/Select.php\t(working copy)\n@@ -78,6 +78,15 @@\n     }\n \n     \/**\n+     * Gets the Zend_Db_Adapter for this particular Zend_Db_Select object.\n+     *\n+     * @return Zend_Db_Adapter_Abstract\n+     *\/\n+    public function getAdapter() {\n+        return $this->_adapter;\n+    }\n+\n+    \/**\n      * Converts this object to an SQL SELECT string.\n      *\n      * @todo use $this->_adapter->quoteColumns() for non-PDO adapters\n{code}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=arikon",
                        "name": "arikon",
                        "displayName": "Sergey Belov",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-02-08T04:51:49.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-02-08T04:51:49.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/12601",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=bkarwin",
                        "name": "bkarwin",
                        "displayName": "Bill Karwin",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I'm not sure I like the use case.  Would something like this be acceptable instead:\n\n{code}\npublic function getData(Zend_Db_Select $dataSource, $limit = null, $offset = null)\n{\n    $dataSource->limit($limit, $offset);\n    $stmt = $dataSource->query();\n    return $stmt->fetchAll();\n}\n{code}\n\nThe implementation in Zend_Db_Select would look something like this:\n{code}\npublic function query($fetchMode = null)\n{\n    $stmt = $this->_adapter->query($this);\n    if ($fetchMode == null) {\n        $fetchMode = $this->_adapter->getFetchMode();\n    }\n    $stmt->setFetchMode($fetchMode);\n    return $stmt;\n}\n{code}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=bkarwin",
                        "name": "bkarwin",
                        "displayName": "Bill Karwin",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-02-08T15:11:34.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-02-08T15:11:34.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/12610",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=arikon",
                        "name": "arikon",
                        "displayName": "Sergey Belov",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Bill, your use case also not bad.\nCan you add query() method to Zend_Db_Select?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=arikon",
                        "name": "arikon",
                        "displayName": "Sergey Belov",
